Getting and Cleaning Data Course Project

Description
1. Collect different set of data related to smartphone fitbit sensors
   subject data, train data, test data, variable names and activity labels
2. Explore the data sets to understand the data and identify steps to produce a tidy data set
3. Manipulte the data to name properly the fields that will be used as parameters to group and summarise the data: activities and variables (=subject)
4. Combined the data in one data set before it can be aggregated
5. Group the data by activity and subject
6. Write the tidy data 

Outcome
They tidy data set requested is a data frame with 180 observationsand 81 variables (str(tidy_data))
It represents the mean of the raw data grouped by activity and subject
